# DOCS_TEST: example_007

query error
SELECT genre, COUNT(*) AS matches, AVG(runtime) AS avg_runtime
FROM movies_idx
WHERE PHRASE(description, 'film')
GROUP BY genre
ORDER BY matches DESC;
----
db error: ERROR: Scalar Function with name phrase does not exist!
Did you mean "<slt:ignore>"?


